G-CHAT-B3-DISPOSER (v10)  ABLATION GATE (Thermodynamic Knockout) — BUILT, RUN, definitive negative
===================================================================================================
The full causal-ablation gate is LIVE and MECHANICALLY CORRECT: CUDA gemma4_kv_ablate_rows
(cudaMemset-zero k episode K/V rows) + glue + Rust FFI kv::ablate + routes SP_B3_DISPOSER=2.
Per candidate: inject E (M=42) -> greedy 8-tok payload -> read ep.tok sidecar -> intersect
payload-window token ids with episode tokens -> ablate those rows -> teacher-force re-score the
SAME payload -> collapse = Σ(LL_ablated - LL_E) over [2,8) -> rewind. Telemetry TAU=-inf (null floor).

THE MATCHER WORKS: ep_homarus query ablated 12 source-token positions; ep_headlam 10. The trapdoor
fired, re-scored, and the O(1) rewind restored cleanly (zero crashes across the 9-query matrix).

